                <head>No. 603.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Baron <persName
                            type="to">Rosen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-10-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 4, 1887</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Secretary of State presents his compliments to the chargé d’affaires <hi
                        rend="italic">ad interim</hi> of Russia, and has the honor to request him to
                    cause the inclosed documents to be authenticated under the seal of the Russian
                    legation and then returned to the Department of State.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
